<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们离开了咖啡店朝着公园走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在公园里看到了很多孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些在操场上，其他的在打棒球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，她在放风筝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简指着拿着红色风筝的一个小女孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是你的女儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坐在长椅上的一个女人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”简觉得疑惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女孩儿，是你女儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个女人又问了一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然不是！”简急切地叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还小，怎么会有孩子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她生气地瞪了那个女人一眼，然后走开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个女人奇怪地看着简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女人对你说了什么？”赛伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她以为我当了妈妈了！”简依然很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是简，”潘瑟温柔地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在已经是个成年人了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还没等简回答，他们就听到了一阵熟悉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是冰淇淋车！”鲍比跳个不停。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为咖啡实在太难喝了。”赛伊咧着嘴笑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该来点甜的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跑着穿过了公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他们的体格更大，速度更快，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们超过了所有的小孩子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个到达了冰淇淋车那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“双份焦糖巧克力软糖，谢谢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比搓着手说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！”司机冷冷地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该让孩子们先买。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着他们身后那些排队的孩子们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先来的。”鲍比固执地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些父母开始非常不客气地批评他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个大男人真不怕羞。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他怎么跟孩子似的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机无奈地耸了耸肩，给了鲍比他的冰淇淋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要一个草莓混合口味的。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是一起工作的吗？”司机问她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我们是一家人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟一边从司机手上拿过冰淇淋一边回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天你们休息？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是什么意思？”潘瑟反问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们今天不工作？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人用愤怒的语气问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“工作？我没有工作啊。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都不工作。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人带着厌恶表情看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该为自己感到羞愧！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有成年人都在努力工作去挣钱，但你们......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着巴斯家的每个孩子：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们就只想要冰淇淋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间冰淇淋就不再那么吸引人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们看看周围，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只看到了一张张愤怒的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可能该走了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们低着头离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们找到一张没人的长椅后，简问：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们为什么对我们这么刻薄？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我们的举止像孩子一样。”潘瑟回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们就是孩子啊。”简争辩说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天不是的，简！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们今天是成年人，记得吗？”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在每个人的眼里，我们都是行为像孩子一样的成年人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们沉默了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着其他的孩子们玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们看上去真开心。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想骑自行车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前觉得当大人会很有意思。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简用力吸了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道当大人会这么难。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐在长椅上，无事可做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊看了看手表，说：“我们回玛莎阿姨家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说：“我们可以藏起来等日落。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我穿着这双鞋没法再走路了。”简嚷嚷着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把高跟鞋扔到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，简。”赛伊说，“我来背你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简爬到了赛伊的背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！你好重！”他喘着气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但赛伊还是像个好哥哥那样背着他的妹妹穿过了公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>路过的人们都停下来盯着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我的天哪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们小声说：“他们在干吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>357927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们不觉得丢人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>